; Regression test for issue #1583: ledger and currency format in entry command (BZ#511)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1583
; The entry command should preserve the commodity format defined in the journal
; (via the D directive or commodity directive) when generating new transactions.

D $1,000.00

2012-03-23 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Groceries    $50.00
    Assets:Checking

; Basic entry preserves commodity format
test --now 2012/03/25 entry "Grocery Store" 100
2012/03/25 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Groceries                       $100.00
    Assets:Checking
end test

; Entry with amount requiring thousands separator
test --now 2012/03/25 entry "Grocery Store" 2500
2012/03/25 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Groceries                     $2,500.00
    Assets:Checking
end test
